&lt;li&gt;Bump renault-api to 0.2.2 (&lt;a href="https://github.com/epenet"&gt;@epenet&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href="https://github.com/home-assistant/core/pull/115738"&gt;#115738&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://www.home-assistant.io/integrations/renault/"&gt;renault docs&lt;/a&gt;) (dependency)&lt;/li&gt;
